sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Clerk as Counter Clerk<br/>(Gulu City Hall)
  participant Rail as Sente Rails<br/>/clerk + /v1
  participant NIRA as NIRA<br/>(via UGHub, sandbox)
  participant MoMo as MTN MoMo<br/>(sandbox live)
  actor Citizen as Mukasa J. P.<br/>(MSISDN +256772...)
  participant Ledger as Gulu City Ledger<br/>(receivable GL)
  participant Verify as Public Verifier<br/>(/verify/{ref})

  Note over Clerk,Rail: Shift open<br/>opening float 100,000 UGX
  Clerk->>Rail: Open shift on GULU

  Note over Clerk,Citizen: Citizen approaches the counter
  Clerk->>Rail: Search NIN CM78001234ABCD
  Rail->>Rail: Cascade local first
  Rail->>NIRA: Identity lookup (stub today, live on cred-land)
  NIRA-->>Rail: Verified - source: NIRA
  Rail-->>Clerk: Mukasa John Patrick (Gulu)

  Clerk->>Rail: Add line - TL-RENEW (50,000 UGX)
  Rail-->>Clerk: Assessment drafted - 1 line - GULU only
  Note right of Rail: efris_taxable=true<br/>FDN attaches on assess

  Clerk->>Rail: Assess - locks the bill
  Rail-->>Clerk: Status: Assessed - print PIN

  Clerk->>Rail: Initiate payment via MoMo
  Rail->>MoMo: requestToPay - 50,000 UGX
  MoMo-->>Citizen: USSD prompt - approve 50,000?
  Citizen-->>MoMo: PIN + approve
  MoMo-->>Rail: Webhook - status=SUCCESSFUL<br/>aggregator txn ref attached

  Rail->>Ledger: Post receivable + journal entry
  Rail->>Rail: Generate QR pointing at /verify/{ref}
  Rail-->>Clerk: Receipt rendered - thermal print + screen

  Note over Citizen,Verify: After leaving the counter
  Citizen->>Verify: Scan QR on printed receipt
  Verify-->>Citizen: PII-safe summary<br/>(MDA, service, amount, date, status)

  Clerk->>Rail: Close shift<br/>cash count = float + cash sales
  Rail-->>Clerk: Variance = 0 - shift sealed
